{"tid":932093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3公斤啞鈴搏殺人犯 俄少年為救母「頭骨全碎」","createTime":"2018-12-07T12:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T06:28:01.000Z","uid":212399,"like":507,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"9457c43f38eabdbbcc638ad030bacc06339832ae","tid":932093,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/07/99/5630977.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F07%2F99%2F5630977.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=33ad2b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凡雅頭部遭兇嫌用啞鈴猛擊，額骨幾乎全碎。<br />\n俄羅斯一名少年某日放學回家，發現母親慘遭有殺人前科的鄰居襲擊，渾身是血。為了救出母親，少年英勇拿起啞鈴與兇嫌搏鬥，但最終遭兇嫌持啞鈴狠砸，額骨幾乎被打碎。少年經歷數月治療，雖一度好轉，近日仍不幸離世。<br />\n據《鏡報》報導，俄羅斯北德文斯克市（Severodvinsk）的一名16歲少年凡雅（Vanya Krapivin），去（2017）年某日放學回家，卻看到他的母親娜塔麗雅（Natalia Krapivina）全身是血躺在地上，而兇嫌正是他們的鄰居羅曼（Roman Pronin）。<br />\n當時，凡雅並沒有逃走，而是拿起3公斤重的啞鈴砸向羅曼。但啞鈴卻被羅曼奪走，凡雅的頭部更遭羅曼持啞鈴猛擊。鄰居聽到騷動後報警，羅曼則以為母子兩人已死，於是逃跑了。<br />\n凡雅和娜塔麗雅被發現時，娜塔麗雅身上有27處刀傷，凡雅則失去了大部分的額骨，腦部也嚴重受創。經急救，娜塔麗雅數月後即出院，但凡雅依然處於昏迷狀態。娜塔麗雅更因為身心大受打擊，僅探望兒子兩次。<br />\n凡雅的英勇事蹟傳開後，俄羅斯的一名節目主持人安德烈（Andrey Malakhov）更推動募資，幫助支付凡雅所需的頭骨重建費用和其他醫療開銷。<br />\n然而，雖然在今（2018）年六、七月，凡雅恢復清醒，也出現好轉的跡象；但十月時，他的病情因流感而惡化。儘管接受重症監護治療，凡雅近日仍不幸離世。<br />\n外媒指出，兇手羅曼曾因兩次殺人未遂罪行而入獄；當他被釋放時，娜塔麗雅便曾向當局反應，不要讓前科犯住在有小孩子的社區。目前，羅曼已遭法院判處14年有期徒刑，如今因凡雅的離世，羅曼也將被依殺人罪起訴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/07/99/5630981.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F07%2F99%2F5630981.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=d36ac372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凡雅為了救出母親，英勇與兇嫌搏鬥。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3523467?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6812%2F3523467%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=54PS%2B4sxISH7eou5KjGTvGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7d6b168d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3523467?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"a533f6036992ea1c82b6ac6fb9dba9708bbd5936","tid":932093,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe43b1b2635f146bab33844c54a0ddd8d1680c8","tid":932093,"uid":70183,"like":921,"dislike":6,"score":915,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"he is hero"},{"pid":"058380446896aa8bfc2a2ea063d7e59eeff0f1f9","tid":932093,"uid":27458,"like":414,"dislike":2,"score":412,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"殺人前科都可以出返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5fe1cea0bc9d0ad3fc23037fc9e56b6f4164f3","tid":932093,"uid":23785,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"e46896a754303359c468f33f21813a2e8841837f","tid":932093,"uid":135313,"like":154,"dislike":4,"score":150,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:01:17.000Z","msg":"痴撚線俄畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6a9ac2538be18f9ace8aaac54794ff0052c2d4","tid":932093,"uid":182210,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44df528a03172a2cfbfd8760f3a36953bc0bb918","tid":932093,"uid":22913,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"058380446896aa8bfc2a2ea063d7e59eeff0f1f9","tid":932093,"uid":27458,"like":414,"dislike":2,"score":412,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"殺人前科都可以出返嚟<img src=\"/asset